descriptionShort: Online AM and FM radio stations from Costa Rica!
title: Radio Costa Rica - Radio FM

creator: Online radios
descriptionHtml:
🇨🇷 Radio Costa Rica is all Costa Rican radios in one application!

- News: Stay informed 24/7 thanks to local, national and global news radios
- Music: Listen to your favorite music, pop, jazz, Latin music, classical music, country or rock on the many musical radios!
- Live sports: Follow your favorite team thanks to sports radios!

And many other themes according to your mood!


🎙️ RADIO STREAMING

With the Radio Costa Rica application, listen live to all your favorite FM, AM or online radios from anywhere in the world!

It's simple, efficient and fast, our radio player is ideal for listening in live stream the most popular radio stations of Costa Rica like Columbia, Omega 105.1, Sinfonola, Bese, Teletica 91.5, Wao 92.3, Disney, Romántica Estéreo, La Caliente 90.7, Recuerdos del Ayer, Urbano 106, Los 40, Uncion 106.7, Super, Clásicos Cost Rica Español and many other radios to discover thanks to our regularly updated suggestions.


📻 APPLICATION FEATURES

☛ Listen live from anywhere in the world
☛ Manage your list of favorite Argentinian radios
☛ Wake-up / alarm function and sleep timer to program the closing of the application
☛ Search function to find a radio
☛ Chromecast and Android Auto compatible
☛ Easily share a radio with your friends!
☛ Application widget for even easier use


🇨🇷 Why Radio Costa Rica?

- Take advantage of a simple and ergonomic interface to offer you an optimal listening experience
- Find your favorites in one click
- No bug. We strive to improve listening quality with each new release


Listen to all Costa Rican radios live, FM AM radio stations and radio online our streaming app!


👍 SUPPORT US

Ads are present in our application, this helps support our great team and continue to offer you a free radio service! But you can switch to the version with no ads displayed with one click;) If you like our application also do not hesitate to leave us a review on the Play Store, thank you 🙂


ℹ️ NEED HELP?

If you want to add radio stations or send us your suggestions write to us at appradios@yahoo.fr


⚠️ Internet connection required, 3G / 4G or Wifi
